https://www.kaggle.com/tmdb/tmdb-movie-metadata?select=tmdb_5000_movies.csv

Type of recommendation system 

1) Content based recommendation : Content-based Filtering is a Machine Learning technique that uses similarities in features to make decisions. 
so here tags are get created and based on similarrites of tags do recommendation system. 
                                    

2) collaborative filtering recommendation system: this method recommend content on the basis of user intrest. 
There are two types: 
a)user-to-user collaborative filtering based on user-to-user similarity. 
b)item-to-item collaborative filtering based on item-to-item similarity.


3) Hybrid recommendation system :

Combination of both recommendation system. 